The victim's mother was seriously injured in the firing and is in hospital in the Aligarth region, NDTV reported.

However, her daughter was pronounced dead at the scene.

The gunmen opened fire before fleeing the area. Police have detained two men for questioning.

It is not clear whether the shooting was carried out at the behest of Teerath, who was accused of raping the woman in 2012 but has never been arrested.

Police say they are also investigating the possibility that another godman, Bhagirathi Baba, was behind the incident.

